    "B. Post-posed shieldsTo provide hard safety guarantees for RL-based methods, one can design preemptive or post-posed shields that can be applied during the training or deploying phase [1], [2].",
    "This paper focuses on implementing post-posed shields for integration at deployment.Let Q * (s, a) represent the optimal action-value function learned during training.",
